 the minimum age of marriage of bridegroom is 21 years.Moreover, the marriage registration certificate must be produced within 1 year of marriage.Applicant must also make self declaration that people will not avail any further assistance from any other board/ dept./ corporation.Also Read \u2013 Haryana Mukhyamantri Mahila Shramik Samman YojanaHaryana Kanyadan Yojana Eligibility CriteriaThe candidates must follow the given eligibility criteria to become eligible for Kanyadan Yojana in Haryana:-Eligibility / \u092a\u093e\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0924\u093eMembership Years / \u0938\u0926\u0938\u094d\u092f\u0924\u093e \u0935\u0930\u094d\u09371 yearsApply Frequency / \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u0940\u092e\u093e3 daughtersScheme For / \u0907\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090fAllContinue After Death / \u092e\u0943\u0924\u094d\u092f\u0941 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0926 \u091c\u093e\u0930\u0940YesPeople will get benefits of Rs. 51,000 before 3 days of their daughter\u2019s marriage.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: hrylabour.gov.in  at  "}